ops::bit::BitAnd::bitand.doc:
Performs the `&` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(true & false, false);
assert_eq!(true & true, true);
assert_eq!(5u8 & 1u8, 1);
assert_eq!(5u8 & 2u8, 0);
```

ops::bit::Not::not.doc:
Performs the unary `!` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(!true, false);
assert_eq!(!false, true);
assert_eq!(!1u8, 254);
assert_eq!(!0u8, 255);
```

ops::bit::BitOr::bitor.doc:
Performs the `|` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(true | false, true);
assert_eq!(false | false, false);
assert_eq!(5u8 | 1u8, 5);
assert_eq!(5u8 | 2u8, 7);
```

